01cO people, the Hajj pilgrimage has been made an obligation, so undertake it.\u201d A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is it every year?\u201d The Prophet remained silent until the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/03\/women-hajj-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":15635,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women performing Hajj will menstruating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, enter my dwelling at Sarif while I was crying. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter? Are you menstruating?\u201d I said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cThis is a matter that Allah has decreed for the daughters of Adam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/hajj-umrah-rewarded-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":15635,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Umrah: Two pilgrimages rewarded with forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe 'Umrah pilgrimage to the following 'Umrah will expiate whatever sins were committed between them, and the blessed Hajj pilgrimage has no reward other than Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\